BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Surf's Up
DTSTART:20260504T085400
DTEND:20260504T130000
DESCRIPTION:TIDES:\n-0.046ft at 08:54\n-2.999ft at 13:00\n\nOBSERVATION:\n
 Nice size blend of NW/WNW swell and some secondary SSW Southern Hemi tops 
 out\, for widespread waist to shoulder high waves\, as top exposures/combo
  breaks are head high+. Draining negative low for the dawn patrol\, then i
 ncoming tide push helps through the morning. \n\nLight/variable winds due 
 much of the morning\, then low-end moderate afternoon SW onshores set up s
 ome lump. 
END:VEVENT
